Once opon a time in a forest, there life a monkey who reicited on a berry tree which was on a bank of a river. 
In the same forest their lived a crocodile and this wife...
One day the crocidile came to the banks of the river and rested under a tree.
The kind hearted Monkey offered him some fruits.
The crocidile came back the next day for more fruits.
As the days past by, Monkey and Crocdile became good friends.